{"tid":853455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼美利堅同不列顛聲之後到歐洲聯盟","createTime":"2018-10-08T15:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T17:17:09.000Z","uid":51620,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4d75ad63fddea4ab2c1ce986d40303f85eff6588","tid":853455,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181008/58769179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769179&d=ytmDTuPZ%2BOZK6zjQ98qKEOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=780961af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769179&h=14af2925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181008/58769179</a><br />\n<br />\n【新增：中國外交部回應】<br />\n任職《金融時報》的外國記者會副主席馬凱被特區政府拒續發工作簽證，繼英國要求港府立即解釋、美國炮轟港府做法不符《基本法》後，今日連歐盟也發聲，質疑有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲聯盟駐港澳辦事處發言人回覆查詢時指，歐盟正密切留意事件，並期望香港政府澄清拒絕向一名記者發出簽證的原因，歐盟又為香港表達和新聞自由本受《基本法》和《公民權利及政治權利國際公約》所保障，如今卻引起一個正式疑問。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟駐港澳辦事處回覆查詢全文：<br />\nThe EU is following this issue closely and expects the HK government to clarify the reasons of the refusal to grant visa to a journalist. This incident raises legitimate questions about the freedom of press and expression in HK, which are guaranteed by HK&rsquo;s Basic Law and ICCPR.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而中國外交部發言人陸慷就強調，香港特區政府是按照《基本法》實行出入境管制，特區政府有權就是否批准在港工作簽證延期申請作出決定，重申權是毋庸置疑，「看不到事件對香港聲譽會產生影響。」"},{"pid":"871889b882bb97eacd1a54cc4c7288430c6419c0","tid":853455,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d183e2339575cb9000f1ad88036b83e6109cd46","tid":853455,"uid":29880,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal